[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gerald Nott death: Woman charged with Coleford man's murder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has been charged with the murder of a pensioner in the Forest of Dean.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gerald Nott, 66, was found dead at a property in Queensway in Broadwell, Coleford, on Sunday morning.
Amanda Howard, 46, from Broadwell, appeared at Cheltenham Magistrates' Court earlier and was remanded in custody.
She is next due to appear before Bristol Crown Court on Thursday, 30 October.
